font.span:
POSSIBLE VOLUME CYCLES
All the initial RENA and ITS comes from each tokens txn tax rewards. We can then route them into any pair we want.
The examples below are if we were to get RENA, Sent all of it to the RENA/rITS pair first, then we use the ITS that we get from people buying RENA to fill up the ITS/rETH pool
I have no idea what this would do to RenaSwap or the volume.
But i think it would increase trading volume and possibly add buy pressure as people would need to buy ITS or RENA to get the best arbitrage options.

- $RENA transaction tax, ability to change it within this range 0% - 20%
- $RENA transaction tax distribution, ability to send any % share to Any contract or RenaSwap Pair. (required to seed new pairs)
- $RENA Max Buy amount, Ability to limit an individuals max buy on uniswap, to stop bots on listing
